title: Prince Harry spotted holding hands with girlfriend Meghan Markle on date in London as pals claim TV star lover has 'virtually moved in' with him
text:
Opinion MEG HAND HARRY Prince Harry spotted holding hands with girlfriend Meghan Markle on date in London as pals claim TV star lover has ‘virtually moved in’ with him 
The loved-up pair have been 'inseparable' for past five weeks and first snaps of the couple hand-in-hand add fuel to friend's claims that they will be 'engaged by spring' Picture exclusive BY EMILY ANDREWS, Royal Correspondent 2nd February 2017, 9:55 pm
